{"tid":1645531,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"(不打自招) 被罵「殺人強姦犯」 蒙面警反譏女街坊：係都唔強姦你啦！","createTime":"2019-10-11T02:21:59.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-11T02:21:59.000Z","uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"c70d7aed58783705e06c8b37c0a920d4ab293f39","tid":1645531,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T02:21:59.000Z","msg":"政府引用《緊急法》硬推《蒙面法》，昨（5日）凌晨開始生效，但仍無阻市民戴口罩上街。有網民發起今午「反緊急法大遊行」，過萬名市民響應號召「行街」塞滿港九多個地區。在大約下午3時，一批持槍防暴警員突然從港鐵灣仔站出口衝出地面，驅散市民。有警員用警棍揮打市民的傘後，登上警車離開。惟街坊不滿多名警員蒙面，指罵他們；有女街坊罵警為「殺人犯、強姦犯」，但有警員情緒失控，反譏對方：「係都唔係強姦你啦！」 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20191006/60123681\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20191006%2F60123681&d=tgdX0zC4r3YoKKw%2Bq%2FbDqbXqul57XbQM8lVYa5HUNM4%3D&h=cdf8beb7\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20191006%2F60123681&h=ea1b6f9b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20191006/60123681</a>"}]}